  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It is important to keep our teeth clean and healthy.",
      "zh": "保持牙齒清潔和健康很重要。",
      "ja": "歯を清潔で健康に保つことは大切です。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So today, I'm visiting the dentist.",
      "zh": "所以今天，我要去看牙醫。",
      "ja": "だから今日は歯医者に行きます。",
      "time": "00:00:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here we are. This is my dentist's office.",
      "zh": "我們到了。這是我的牙醫診所。",
      "ja": "着きました。ここが私の歯医者の診療所です。",
      "time": "00:00:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I wore a special shirt.",
      "zh": "我穿了一件特別的襯衫。",
      "ja": "特別なシャツを着ました。",
      "time": "00:00:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's go check in.",
      "zh": "我們去報到吧。",
      "ja": "受付に行きましょう。",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi, I'm Katie.",
      "zh": "嗨，我是凱蒂。",
      "ja": "こんにちは、ケイティです。",
      "time": "00:00:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm here to see my dentist's Kathy.",
      "zh": "我來看我的牙醫凱西。",
      "ja": "歯医者のキャシーに会いに来ました。",
      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nice to see you again, Katie.",
      "zh": "很高興再次見到你，凱蒂。",
      "ja": "また会えて嬉しいよ、ケイティ。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nice to see you.",
      "zh": "很高興見到你。",
      "ja": "会えて嬉しいです。",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Kathy will be with you in a few moments.",
      "zh": "凱西馬上就會來找你。",
      "ja": "キャシーがすぐに来ますよ。",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "If you'd like to have a seat in the waiting room to wait for her.",
      "zh": "你可以在候診室坐著等她。",
      "ja": "待合室でお待ちください。",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, great. Thank you.",
      "zh": "好的，太好了。謝謝。",
      "ja": "はい、ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So we can wait here until it's our turn.",
      "zh": "我們可以在這裡等候輪到我們。",
      "ja": "順番が来るまでここで待てます。",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sometimes in the waiting room, there's magazines and toys too.",
      "zh": "候診室裡有時候也有雜誌和玩具。",
      "ja": "待合室には時々雑誌やおもちゃもあります。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hi, Katie.",
      "zh": "嗨，凱蒂。",
      "ja": "こんにちは、ケイティ。",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you ready for your dental?",
      "zh": "你準備好看牙了嗎？",
      "ja": "歯科の準備はできましたか？",
      "time": "00:00:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi, Kathy.",
      "zh": "嗨，凱西。",
      "ja": "こんにちは、キャシー。",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is Kathy, my dentist.",
      "zh": "這是凱西，我的牙醫。",
      "ja": "こちらは私の歯医者のキャシーです。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "A dentist is a special person who looks after our teeth.",
      "zh": "牙醫是照顧我們牙齒的專業人士。",
      "ja": "歯医者は私たちの歯をケアする特別な人です。",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's right.",
      "zh": "沒錯。",
      "ja": "その通りです。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And Kathy has been looking after my teeth for a long time.",
      "zh": "凱西照顧我的牙齒很久了。",
      "ja": "キャシーは長い間私の歯を見てくれています。",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Since she was a little girl.",
      "zh": "從她還是小女孩的時候。",
      "ja": "彼女が小さな女の子の時からです。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Real little.",
      "zh": "非常小的時候。",
      "ja": "本当に小さい頃から。",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So come on back and we'll do them today.",
      "zh": "那我們進去，今天來檢查牙齒吧。",
      "ja": "さあ戻って、今日の治療をしましょう。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great. Thank you.",
      "zh": "太好了，謝謝。",
      "ja": "いいですね。ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Katie, come on in.",
      "zh": "凱蒂，進來吧。",
      "ja": "ケイティ、入ってください。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You remember my special chair?",
      "zh": "你還記得我的特別椅子嗎？",
      "ja": "私の特別な椅子を覚えていますか？",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "zh": "喔，記得。",
      "ja": "はい、覚えています。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I remember this chair.",
      "zh": "我記得這張椅子。",
      "ja": "この椅子を覚えています。",
      "time": "00:01:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This chair goes up and down and back and forth.",
      "zh": "這張椅子可以上下移動，也可以前後移動。",
      "ja": "この椅子は上下に動き、前後にも動きます。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Remember that?",
      "zh": "還記得嗎？",
      "ja": "覚えていますか？",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "He's loved to do this when you were a little girl.",
      "zh": "你小時候很喜歡這樣做。",
      "ja": "あなたが小さな女の子の時にこれをするのが好きでしたね。",
      "time": "00:01:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So far.",
      "zh": "到目前為止。",
      "ja": "今のところ。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And back and forth, it moves in many different directions.",
      "zh": "它可以前後移動，也能多方向調整。",
      "ja": "前後に動き、多方向に調整できます。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So I can adjust it so I can see perfectly.",
      "zh": "我可以調整它，讓我能完美地看清楚。",
      "ja": "完璧に見えるように調整できます。",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "素晴らしい。",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So let's put you back.",
      "zh": "那我們讓你躺下。",
      "ja": "では、背もたれを倒しましょう。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:01:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, and I remember this is a special light.",
      "zh": "喔，我記得這是特別的燈光。",
      "ja": "ああ、これは特別なライトですね。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's a very special light.",
      "zh": "這是一盞非常特別的燈。",
      "ja": "とても特別なライトです。",
      "time": "00:01:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Because if I want to look in your mouth, it's a pretty small space.",
      "zh": "因為如果我要看你的嘴巴，那是個很小的空間。",
      "ja": "口の中を見るには、とても狭い空間だからです。",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And it's dark and I can't see very well with my special light.",
      "zh": "而且裡面很暗，用我的特別燈光才能看清楚。",
      "ja": "暗くて、特別なライトがないとよく見えません。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can see.",
      "zh": "我能看見。",
      "ja": "見えます。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, I'm very well.",
      "zh": "喔，我看得很清楚。",
      "ja": "ああ、とてもよく見えます。",
      "time": "00:01:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's bright.",
      "zh": "很亮。",
      "ja": "明るいです。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is bright.",
      "zh": "是的，很亮。",
      "ja": "明るいですね。",
      "time": "00:01:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But before we do all that, we need our safety equipment.",
      "zh": "但在做這些之前，我們需要安全裝備。",
      "ja": "でもその前に、安全装備が必要です。",
      "time": "00:01:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, for you and me.",
      "zh": "喔，為了你和我。",
      "ja": "ああ、あなたと私のためですね。",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Safety glasses for you.",
      "zh": "給你戴安全眼鏡。",
      "ja": "あなたには安全メガネを。",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, safety glasses for me to protect our eyes.",
      "zh": "喔，給我戴安全眼鏡來保護我們的眼睛。",
      "ja": "ああ、私も目を守るために安全メガネをかけます。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And the next thing we need is my mask.",
      "zh": "接著我們需要我的口罩。",
      "ja": "次に必要なのは私のマスクです。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And then I put on my gloves.",
      "zh": "然後我戴上手套。",
      "ja": "そして手袋をつけます。",
      "time": "00:02:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So you have the mask and the glasses and gloves.",
      "zh": "所以你有口罩、眼鏡和手套。",
      "ja": "だからマスクとメガネと手袋があります。",
      "time": "00:02:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Also, we don't get germs.",
      "zh": "而且我們不會感染細菌。",
      "ja": "それに、細菌に感染しません。",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "zh": "沒錯。",
      "ja": "その通りです。",
      "time": "00:02:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, Katie.",
      "zh": "好的，凱蒂。",
      "ja": "はい、ケイティ。",
      "time": "00:02:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So let's clean your teeth.",
      "zh": "那我們來清潔你的牙齒。",
      "ja": "では、歯をきれいにしましょう。",
      "time": "00:02:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you ready?",
      "zh": "你準備好了嗎？",
      "ja": "準備はいいですか？",
      "time": "00:02:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ready.",
      "zh": "準備好了。",
      "ja": "準備できました。",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "很好。",
      "ja": "いいですね。",
      "time": "00:02:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So let's get my nice bright light so I can see.",
      "zh": "那我打開明亮的燈光，讓我能看清楚。",
      "ja": "明るいライトをつけてよく見ましょう。",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And here are my instruments.",
      "zh": "這是我的工具。",
      "ja": "こちらが私の器具です。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "よし。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's start with your front teeth.",
      "zh": "我們從你的前牙開始。",
      "ja": "前歯から始めましょう。",
      "time": "00:02:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Open wide like a lion.",
      "zh": "張大嘴巴，像獅子一樣。",
      "ja": "ライオンのように大きく開けて。",
      "time": "00:02:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, you'd make a very good lion.",
      "zh": "喔，你會是一隻很棒的獅子。",
      "ja": "ああ、あなたはとても良いライオンになれますね。",
      "time": "00:02:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You can open very wide.",
      "zh": "你可以張得很大。",
      "ja": "とても大きく開けますね。",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And now I'm going to start.",
      "zh": "現在我要開始了。",
      "ja": "さあ、始めますよ。",
      "time": "00:02:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How does that feel?",
      "zh": "感覺如何？",
      "ja": "どう感じますか？",
      "time": "00:02:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "很好。",
      "ja": "いいです。",
      "time": "00:02:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And the good news is you're looking very good.",
      "zh": "好消息是你的牙齒看起來非常好。",
      "ja": "良い知らせは、あなたの歯はとても良い状態です。",
      "time": "00:02:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It looks to me like you're brushing them, are you?",
      "zh": "看起來你有在刷牙，是嗎？",
      "ja": "歯を磨いているようですね、そうですか？",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yep.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Twice a day, morning and night.",
      "zh": "一天兩次，早晚各一次。",
      "ja": "一日二回、朝と夜に。",
      "time": "00:02:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That is wonderful.",
      "zh": "那真是太好了。",
      "ja": "それは素晴らしいです。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good for you.",
      "zh": "做得好。",
      "ja": "よくできました。",
      "time": "00:03:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And what about floss to clean between them?",
      "zh": "那你有用牙線清潔牙縫嗎？",
      "ja": "歯の間を掃除するフロスは使っていますか？",
      "time": "00:03:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you using that?",
      "zh": "你有用嗎？",
      "ja": "使っていますか？",
      "time": "00:03:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯嗯。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:03:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I try.",
      "zh": "我有嘗試。",
      "ja": "やっています。",
      "time": "00:03:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good girl.",
      "zh": "乖孩子。",
      "ja": "いい子ですね。",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's important to try to do that every day to keep them very clean.",
      "zh": "每天嘗試這樣做很重要，能保持牙齒非常乾淨。",
      "ja": "毎日それをするように努力することが大切です。",
      "time": "00:03:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:03:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So now that we've cleaned your teeth, now it's time to polish them.",
      "zh": "現在我們已經清潔了你的牙齒，接下來是拋光。",
      "ja": "歯をきれいにしたので、今度は磨きます。",
      "time": "00:03:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you ready for that?",
      "zh": "你準備好了嗎？",
      "ja": "準備はいいですか？",
      "time": "00:03:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:03:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:03:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And you remember my polisher?",
      "zh": "你還記得我的拋光機嗎？",
      "ja": "私のポリッシャーを覚えていますか？",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It has a little rubber wheel on the end, which is very soft and gentle.",
      "zh": "它的末端有一個小橡膠輪，非常柔軟且溫和。",
      "ja": "先端に小さなゴムの車輪があり、とても柔らかく優しいです。",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now we'll put a little polish on.",
      "zh": "現在我們會塗上一點拋光劑。",
      "ja": "今から少し研磨剤をつけます。",
      "time": "00:03:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And I almost forgot.",
      "zh": "我差點忘了。",
      "ja": "忘れるところでした。",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Mr. Slurpy.",
      "zh": "史拉比先生。",
      "ja": "スラーピーさん。",
      "time": "00:03:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We need him.",
      "zh": "我們需要他。",
      "ja": "彼が必要です。",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Mr. Slurpy.",
      "zh": "史拉比先生。",
      "ja": "スラーピーさん。",
      "time": "00:03:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Because they're saliva in your mouth.",
      "zh": "因為你口中有唾液。",
      "ja": "口の中に唾液があるからです。",
      "time": "00:03:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It gets in my way when I'm trying to polish.",
      "zh": "當我想拋光時，它會妨礙我。",
      "ja": "磨こうとするときに邪魔になります。",
      "time": "00:03:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So it's just slurpy.",
      "zh": "所以就用史拉比。",
      "ja": "だからスラーピーを使います。",
      "time": "00:03:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Turns on.",
      "zh": "打開。",
      "ja": "スイッチを入れます。",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And it's like a straw.",
      "zh": "它像吸管一樣。",
      "ja": "ストローのようなものです。",
      "time": "00:03:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's suction.",
      "zh": "它是吸力裝置。",
      "ja": "吸引装置です。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's the saliva way.",
      "zh": "是吸走唾液的裝置。",
      "ja": "唾液を吸い取ります。",
      "time": "00:03:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "If I took a little cup, put some water in the cup.",
      "zh": "如果我拿一個小杯子，倒一些水進去。",
      "ja": "小さなカップに水を入れてみます。",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You can see how it actually works.",
      "zh": "你可以看到它是怎麼運作的。",
      "ja": "実際にどう動くか見てみましょう。",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "See how it's taking a while?",
      "zh": "看它怎麼吸水？",
      "ja": "吸い込む様子が見えますか？",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, the water?",
      "zh": "喔，水嗎？",
      "ja": "ああ、水ですか？",
      "time": "00:03:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:03:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's like an elephant trunk.",
      "zh": "它像大象的鼻子。",
      "ja": "象の鼻のようです。",
      "time": "00:03:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It is.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "そうです。",
      "time": "00:03:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Water gone.",
      "zh": "水被吸走了。",
      "ja": "水がなくなりました。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:03:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Up the slurpy.",
      "zh": "史拉比吸走了。",
      "ja": "スラーピーが吸い取ります。",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So that's what we're going to do.",
      "zh": "所以我們就這麼做。",
      "ja": "だからこれを使います。",
      "time": "00:04:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:04:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:04:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So I'll use it back.",
      "zh": "我會用它在後面。",
      "ja": "後ろで使います。",
      "time": "00:04:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll put my nice bright light so I can see what I'm doing.",
      "zh": "我會打開明亮的燈光，讓我看得清楚。",
      "ja": "明るいライトをつけてよく見ます。",
      "time": "00:04:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And open and Mr. Slurpy into your mouth.",
      "zh": "張開嘴巴，史拉比放進你的嘴裡。",
      "ja": "口を開けて、スラーピーを口に入れます。",
      "time": "00:04:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And let's polish them.",
      "zh": "我們來拋光牙齒。",
      "ja": "歯を磨きましょう。",
      "time": "00:04:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We'll start in the back corner there.",
      "zh": "我們從後面的角落開始。",
      "ja": "後ろの隅から始めます。",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How's that?",
      "zh": "感覺如何？",
      "ja": "どうですか？",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It kind of tickles.",
      "zh": "有點癢癢的。",
      "ja": "ちょっとくすぐったいです。",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, really?",
      "zh": "喔，真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本当ですか？",
      "time": "00:04:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You notice that?",
      "zh": "你注意到了嗎？",
      "ja": "気づきましたか？",
      "time": "00:04:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And then we use a little bit more.",
      "zh": "然後我們再多用一點。",
      "ja": "それからもう少し使います。",
      "time": "00:04:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And around we go until we have all of the teeth polished.",
      "zh": "繞著牙齒轉，直到所有牙齒都拋光完成。",
      "ja": "ぐるっと回してすべての歯を磨きます。",
      "time": "00:04:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There, teeth polished.",
      "zh": "好了，牙齒拋光完成。",
      "ja": "はい、歯が磨かれました。",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And now all that gritty taste will let you rinse out.",
      "zh": "現在你可以漱口，去除那種沙沙的味道。",
      "ja": "今、ざらざらした味を洗い流しましょう。",
      "time": "00:04:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So I'll put my mirror up.",
      "zh": "我會舉起鏡子。",
      "ja": "鏡を持ち上げます。",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, okay.",
      "zh": "喔，好。",
      "ja": "ああ、わかりました。",
      "time": "00:04:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Put the chair.",
      "zh": "把椅子調整好。",
      "ja": "椅子を戻します。",
      "time": "00:04:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's easy.",
      "zh": "那很簡單。",
      "ja": "簡単ですね。",
      "time": "00:04:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:04:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And you can have a drink.",
      "zh": "你可以喝水。",
      "ja": "飲み物をどうぞ。",
      "time": "00:04:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And then soap.",
      "zh": "然後漱口。",
      "ja": "そしてうがいをします。",
      "time": "00:04:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, they look fantastic.",
      "zh": "喔，它們看起來很棒。",
      "ja": "ああ、とてもきれいになりました。",
      "time": "00:05:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good for you.",
      "zh": "做得好。",
      "ja": "よくできました。",
      "time": "00:05:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now we can take off all of my gloves here.",
      "zh": "現在我可以脫掉手套了。",
      "ja": "これで手袋を外します。",
      "time": "00:05:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let me take those from you.",
      "zh": "讓我幫你拿掉。",
      "ja": "取ってあげますね。",
      "time": "00:05:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You don't need them.",
      "zh": "你不需要戴手套。",
      "ja": "手袋は必要ありません。",
      "time": "00:05:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But one more thing.",
      "zh": "但還有一件事。",
      "ja": "でももう一つあります。",
      "time": "00:05:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You need a new toothbrush.",
      "zh": "你需要一把新的牙刷。",
      "ja": "新しい歯ブラシが必要です。",
      "time": "00:05:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "zh": "喔，對。",
      "ja": "ああ、そうですね。",
      "time": "00:05:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You get a toothbrush when you come to the dentist.",
      "zh": "你來看牙醫時會拿到牙刷。",
      "ja": "歯医者に来ると歯ブラシがもらえます。",
      "time": "00:05:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You do.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "そうです。",
      "time": "00:05:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But what color do you want?",
      "zh": "但你想要什麼顏色？",
      "ja": "どの色が欲しいですか？",
      "time": "00:05:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's see.",
      "zh": "讓我看看。",
      "ja": "見てみましょう。",
      "time": "00:05:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There's orange, green.",
      "zh": "有橘色、綠色。",
      "ja": "オレンジ、グリーンがあります。",
      "time": "00:05:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll use my favorite color.",
      "zh": "我會選我最喜歡的顏色。",
      "ja": "好きな色を選びます。",
      "time": "00:05:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, then blow it is.",
      "zh": "喔，那就是藍色了。",
      "ja": "ああ、それなら青ですね。",
      "time": "00:05:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There you go.",
      "zh": "給你。",
      "ja": "はい、どうぞ。",
      "time": "00:05:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you very much.",
      "zh": "非常感謝。",
      "ja": "どうもありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:05:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And you need a floss.",
      "zh": "你還需要牙線。",
      "ja": "フロスも必要ですね。",
      "time": "00:05:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろんです。",
      "time": "00:05:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's give you one of those too.",
      "zh": "我們也給你一條牙線。",
      "ja": "それもあげましょう。",
      "time": "00:05:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks, Kathy.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，凱西。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、キャシー。",
      "time": "00:05:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You are very welcome.",
      "zh": "不客氣。",
      "ja": "どういたしまして。",
      "time": "00:05:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So your dental appointment is done.",
      "zh": "你的牙科預約完成了。",
      "ja": "歯科の診察は終わりました。",
      "time": "00:05:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So let's go on out to the front.",
      "zh": "那我們去前面吧。",
      "ja": "では、前に行きましょう。",
      "time": "00:05:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We'll finish up.",
      "zh": "我們結束了。",
      "ja": "終わりにしましょう。",
      "time": "00:05:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "素晴らしい。",
      "time": "00:05:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Katie, it was so nice to see you.",
      "zh": "凱蒂，很高興見到你。",
      "ja": "ケイティ、会えてとても嬉しかったです。",
      "time": "00:05:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "As I see it too.",
      "zh": "我也是。",
      "ja": "私もです。",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look forward to seeing you again.",
      "zh": "期待再次見到你。",
      "ja": "また会えるのを楽しみにしています。",
      "time": "00:05:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bye.",
      "zh": "再見。",
      "ja": "さようなら。",
      "time": "00:05:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Bye.",
      "zh": "再見。",
      "ja": "さようなら。",
      "time": "00:05:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bye.",
      "zh": "再見。",
      "ja": "さようなら。",
      "time": "00:05:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All done.",
      "zh": "全部完成了。",
      "ja": "すべて終わりました。",
      "time": "00:06:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now my teeth are clean and healthy.",
      "zh": "現在我的牙齒乾淨又健康。",
      "ja": "今、私の歯はきれいで健康です。",
      "time": "00:06:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, everybody.",
      "zh": "大家好。",
      "ja": "みなさん、こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:06:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's Katie.",
      "zh": "我是凱蒂。",
      "ja": "ケイティです。",
      "time": "00:06:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks for joining us today.",
      "zh": "謝謝你今天加入我們。",
      "ja": "今日は参加してくれてありがとう。",
      "time": "00:06:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'd love it if you would subscribe to our Katie's classroom channel.",
      "zh": "如果你能訂閱我們的凱蒂教室頻道，我會很開心。",
      "ja": "私たちのケイティの教室チャンネルを登録してくれると嬉しいです。",
      "time": "00:06:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I'll see you soon.",
      "zh": "我們很快再見。",
      "ja": "またすぐに会いましょう。",
      "time": "00:06:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Woo.",
      "zh": "耶。",
      "ja": "やったー。",
      "time": "00:06:17"
    }
  ]
}